
recordmydesktop (tested with recordmydesktop-0.3.8.1)
KDE-4.3 or KDE-4.4
JoschyCore: http://gitorious.org/joschy/joschy

Optional:
    ffmepg for ffmpeg encoder plugin                                  // buildtime
    mencoder (part of mplayer) for mencoder encoder plugin            // buildtime
    XFixes for the "Draw the cursor" option in the screenshot plugin  // buildtime
